       Step 2 — Chord Awareness (4 minutes) 
       Exercise: 
       Arpeggios over chord progression 
       Example: 
       Dm7 → G7 → Cmaj7 
       Goal: 
       Understand chord tones. 
                                             
       Step 3 — Guide Tone Practice (4 minutes) 
       Exercise: 
       Guide tone lines 
       Example: 
       F → B → E 
       Goal: 
       Hear the movement between chords. 
                                             
       Step 4 — Jazz Line Practice (5 minutes) 
       Exercise: 
       Bebop line or target tone exercise. 
       Goal: 
       Develop improvisation vocabulary. 
                                             
       Step 5 — Creative Exercise (5 minutes) 
       Exercise: 
       Call and response or motif development. 
       Goal: 
       Encourage musical thinking and improvisation. 
                                             
